   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtschaftsweisung für Hans Goczman und Katharina, Gattin des Stephan Röt/ein</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> 2 Einbr. 2 Zg. (Indez: Item frewntschaft frawn Golden Ulreichs witib am Ort) <rs
                  type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_487">Des nachsten erigtags nach sand Luceyn tag <rs
                     type="fn" role="witness">komen fur den rat <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__johann_gozmann_StB_I_487">Hanns Goczman</rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_487"><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName>
                        Kathrey, <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__stephan_roetel_StB_I_487"
                              ><add>hawsfraw</add></roleName><rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__stephan_roetel_StB_I_487">Stephans hawsfraw des Rötleins</rs>,
                        sein <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_gozmann_StB_I_487"
                           >swester</roleName></rs>, und habent da beweist mit den erbern lewten,
                     als si ze recht solten</rs>, daz <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__johann_gozmann_StB_I_487">ir</rs><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_487"><add>ir</add></rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="issuer" cert="high"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__gold_StB_I_63"
                           ><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_gozmann_StB_I_487"
                           >muter</roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_487"
                              ><add>muter</add></roleName><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName>
                        Gold, <roleName type="dead">weilent</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__ulrich_an_dem_ort_StB_I_63"
                              ><add>witib</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__gundolt_StB_I_63"><add>rechte
                           geswistreid</add></roleName><rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__ulrich_an_dem_ort_StB_I_63">Ulreichs <roleName type="dead"
                              >witib</roleName> am Ort</rs></rs></rs>, und <rs type="fn"
                     role="issuer" cert="high"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__gundolt_StB_I_63">Gundolt
                        von Elpeltaw <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__gold_StB_I_63"><add>rechte
                              geswistreid</add></roleName></rs> zway rechte geswistreid gewesen sind
                     von vater und von muter.</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="witness">Als darumb die obgenanten erbern lewt <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__peter_pleuel_StB_I_487"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Peter der Plewl</rs> und <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__martin_goeschl_StB_I_487"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Mert der Göschel</rs> mit iren trewen an
                     aydes stat vor offem rat habent gesagt, als si ze recht solten</rs>.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
